---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-pine border-t border-forest/50 mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">🏔️</span>
          <span class="font-display text-xl text-cream font-bold">Idaho Gear Guide</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-sage leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Honest, locally-tested gear recommendations for North Idaho's outdoor enthusiasts. We paddle the lakes, hike the trails, and fish the rivers so you can gear up with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-mono text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Explore</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/gear-picks" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Gear Picks</a></li>
          <li><a href="/coeur-dalene" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Coeur d'Alene</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sandpoint" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Sandpoint</a></li>
          <li><a href="/priest-lake" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Priest Lake</a></li>
          <li><a href="/schweitzer-mountain" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Schweitzer</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-mono text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Resources</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/about" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/newsletter" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Newsletter</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/lake-coeur-dalene-summer-outdoor-guide" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Summer Guide</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/best-fishing-spots-lake-coeur-dalene" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Fishing Guide</a></li>
          <li><a href="/disclosure" class="font-body text-sm text-moss hover:text-cream transition-colors">Affiliate Disclosure</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-forest/50 mt-8 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-sage">
        &copy; {currentYear} Idaho Gear Guide. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-xs text-sage/70">
        Affiliate disclosure: We earn commissions from qualifying purchases. This doesn't affect our recommendations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
